From 2ce473c20354551133146385848066ffadef7457 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: HONG Yifan <elsk@google.com>
Date: Fri, 18 Jul 2025 23:07:15 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] Add local.bzl.

Originally from
https://cs.android.com/android/kernel/superproject/+/common-android-mainline:build/kernel/kleaf/impl/local_repository.bzl
hence licence header is kept.

This replaces @bazel_tools//cuttlefish/bazel:local.bzl to address
https://github.com/bazelbuild/bazel/issues/26578
---
 local.bzl | 65 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 65 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 local.bzl

diff --git a/local.bzl b/local.bzl
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..40e5686
--- /dev/null
+++ b/local.bzl
@@ -0,0 +1,65 @@
